### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Terraform Backend API – State & Lock Operations
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Select 'local' in Rider dropdown
### Auth: Basic (via {{authHeader}})
### Tenant: {{tenant}} (from env)
### Base: {{baseUrl}}
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Rider settings: in HTTP Client, uncheck "Variable should be double-quoted" (File | Settings | Editor | Inspection Settings | Inspection Severity | Other Languages)

### Health Check (auxiliary endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### OpenAPI JSON (auxiliary)
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### Scalar UI (auxiliary – open in browser after running)
GET {{baseUrl}}/scalar
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### GET State (read)
### Expected: 200 (state as text/plain) or 404 (not found)
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Accept: text/plain

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### POST State (create/update) – Without Lock (should fail if locked)
### Expected: 200 (empty) or 423 (locked) if no/missing lock
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{{stateBody}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### LOCK State (create lock)
### Expected: 200 (lock info) or 423 (already locked)
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}/lock
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Id": "{{lockId}}",
  "Operation": "Operation.apply",
  "Info": "Applying changes from CI",
  "Who": "ci-user@build-123",
  "Version": "1.9.0",
  "Created": "2026-02-25T14:30:00Z",
  "Path": "terraform.tfstate"
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### POST State (create/update) – With Valid Lock ID
### Expected: 200 if lock matches
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}?ID={{lockId}}
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{{stateBody}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### DELETE State – With Valid Lock ID
### Expected: 200 if lock matches
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}?ID={{lockId}}
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### UNLOCK State (delete lock)
### Expected: 200 (idempotent)
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}/lock
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Id": "{{lockId}}"
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Error Case: POST State – With Wrong Lock ID (conflict)
### Expected: 409 (conflict)
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}?ID=wrong-lock-id-999
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{{stateBody}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Error Case: DELETE State – Without Lock ID (should fail)
### Expected: 423 (locked) if state is locked
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Error Case: DELETE State – Without Wrong Lock ID (should fail)
### Expected: 409 (conflict)
### ────────────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{tenant}}/state/{{stateName}}?ID=wrong-lock-id-999
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

